## Quick Reference Card

### Navigation:
- `context.goNamed(AppRoute.routeName, pathParameters: {'id': value})`
- KHÔNG dùng `Navigator.push()`

### State:
- `ref.watch()` trong UI (reactive)
- `ref.read()` trong callbacks (one-time)
- Dùng `@riverpod` annotation

### Design:
- `DesignColors.*` thay vì `Color(0xFF...)`
- `DesignSpacing.*` + `Gap()` thay vì `SizedBox`
- `DesignTypography.*` thay vì `TextStyle(fontSize: 14)`

### Errors:
- `AppLogger` thay vì `print()`
- `AsyncValue.guard()` trong Notifier
- Báo cáo Sentry cho critical flows

### Code Quality:
- Functions: max 50 lines
- Classes: max 300 lines
- `const` constructors when possible
- `flutter analyze` + `dart format` trước commit
